imdb.plot outline: Episode 1 "PROBLEMS" : Range Day-1. We demonstrate M&P-1O issues and challenges encountered, and discuss possible solutions from viewer comments and observations in other TSF Channel episodes. Episode 2 "APEX HANDGUARD INSTALL": At the Gun Labs. We install an APEX MACHINING 2360 AR10/308 DPMS 15.0" GatorGrip Handguard in an attempt to free-float the M&P-10 barrel. Also installed is a VLTOR clamp on mini gas block. Detailed installation. Episode 3 "RESULTS": Range Day - 2. You will be a believer. We review lessons learned from the mod in Episode 2, "The Gun Labs." Then baptize by fire our newborn SAPR at our secret desert range complex.
